ed 4<b>."},{"content":"Divide prawns between Varoma dish and tray. Place Varoma into position, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>5 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Stir with spatula to ensure even cooking, then secure Varoma lid and steam <b>3-5 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>, until prawns are cooked to your liking. Transfer prawns into a bowl, add reserved parsley butter and toss to coat. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and transfer rice onto a large serving plate. Place prawns on top of rice, drizzle with a few tablespoons of the reserved oil and serve with remaining oil and lemon wedges."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Ask your fishmonger to devein and butterfly your prawns for you.","The chilli oil can be made up to 1 week in advance and stored in the refrigerator to boost flavour and colours."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 10m","4 portions"]}